message.body: Hey ##### it's ################said you may be interested in some work. What kind of availability do you have these days?
Hi #######, I'm busy on Tuesday installing a show at a gallery. Other than that my other work is flexible so I can help you out whenever you need. Thanks for thinking of me
No problem ####### will be in touch as the time grows near.
Well that was fast... Can you come at 9am on Thurs feb 27&fri 28th?
Yeah, where am I coming in to?
i will be more excited if there are actual snakes
I will see what i can do.
Great thanks, I am always more motivated when working in stimulating environments.
